title: They Said What?!: Find Out What Ariana Grande, David Blaine, And Shailene Woodley Have To Say
text: Like Ever wonder what’s on the mind of today’s most notable people? Well, don’t miss our unbelievable roundup of the best and most talked about quotes of the day: “ Sedimentary rocks make up about 90 percent of the rock we see every day. So if you a see a photo of me in a magazine looking delirious and pumping my fist, I am most likely walking on essexite rock, which is rare. ” —Ariana Grande On paparazzi photos “ Every magician has his or her own secrets, but the rule of thumb is that if you can get an animal to chew in an exaggerated manner, you’ve got an opportunity to make it look like that animal is talking. ” —David Blaine On magic “ Burning trash actually isn’t all that bad if you inhale all of the toxic fumes before they reach the ozone layer. ” —Shailene Woodley
